Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:56.95,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}UN-DELAYED, Fallin' fallin' love now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:01:02.49,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}這就是命中注定…Oh my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:10.17,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不會讓你說你沒聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:11.67,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}1,2…heart beat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:15.51,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在星辰大海中唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:19.01,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只屬於我的命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:22.47,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}若是動了真情  怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:21.47,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(你又會)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:25.39,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用盡全心全意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:28.69,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去尋找未來的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:36.57,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在你那裡找到了  不會消去的夢之所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:42.41,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}假如世界停轉一天的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.79,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(在停轉之時)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:49.88,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}請一直一直抱緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:49.88,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(緊緊抱著我)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:53.09,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}盡想著這些任性的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:56.84,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}對不起…喜歡你「沒有極限」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:00.76,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不要害怕  明天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.13,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(1,2 heart!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:01.55,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(1,2 beat!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.01,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}希望可以確認你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:04.77,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(UN-DELAYED)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:12.36,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用觸及的指尖接受我熱情的奇蹟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.36,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}UN-DELAYED, Oh my love!
